Package org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain

Class LipidAdduct

java.lang.Object
org.lifstools.jgoslin.domain.LipidAdduct
public final class LipidAdduct extends Object
Base class for lipid names parsed using the different grammars. This can contain a lipid, an adduct and a sum formula.
Author:
Dominik Kopczynski, Nils Hoffmann
